== 私人生活 ==
瑪格麗特在大学期间遇到了后来的丈夫，詹姆斯·汉密尔顿（{{lang|en|James Cox Hamilton}}; 1937-2014），五十年代末瑪格麗特毕业后两人结婚，育有一个女儿，二人最终离婚<ref name=JCH_obit>{{lang|en|{{cite news |last1=Stickgold |first1=Emma |title=James Cox Hamilton, at 77; lawyer was quiet warrior for First Amendment |url=http://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2014/08/30/james-cox-hamilton-mentor-young-lawyers-also-handled-aclu-cases/CGoF5qLYsNnUEap7BuTrGJ/story.html |accessdate=2015-07-05 |work=Boston Globe |date=2014-08-31 |language=en |archive-date=2015-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706162357/http://www.bostonglobe.com/metro/2014/08/30/james-cox-hamilton-mentor-young-lawyers-also-handled-aclu-cases/CGoF5qLYsNnUEap7BuTrGJ/story.html |dead-url=no }}}}</ref>。

